{
  "macro_id": "plumbing.waterHeaterSize",
  "domain": "plumbing",
  "name": "waterHeaterSize",
  "inputs": {
    "household": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "simultaneousFixtures": {
      "type": "number"
    },
    "tempRiseF": {
      "type": "number"
    }
  },
  "reads_artifact_data": true,
  "invariants": [
    "typeof output === 'object' && output !== null",
    "typeof output.ok === 'boolean'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.household)",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.peakDemandGPM)",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.tankRecommendation === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.tanklessRecommendation === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(output.result.firstHourRating)",
    "output.ok === false || typeof output.result.recommendation === 'string'",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(parseFloat(output.result.tanklessRecommendation))",
    "output.ok === false || Number.isFinite(parseFloat(output.result.tankRecommendation))"
  ],
  "fuzz_cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "household": 4,
            "simultaneousFixtures": 2
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "household": 6,
            "simultaneousFixtures": 3
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {}
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": true
      }
    },
    {
      "input": {
        "artifact": {
          "data": {
            "household": "x",
            "simultaneousFixtures": "NaN",
            "tempRiseF": "Infinity"
          }
        }
      },
      "expect": {
        "ok": false
      }
    }
  ],
  "_note": "Pure compute, reads artifact.data. peakGPM = simultaneous·2.5 ; tank = ceil(people·15/10)·10 gal ; tankless kW = round(peakGPM·8.33·60·ΔT/3412) (ΔT default 70°F, overridable via tempRiseF) ; firstHour = round(tank·1.5). Non-finite household/fixtures/ΔT fall to defaults (2/2/70) via Number.isFinite guards — Infinity ΔT no longer leaks an 'Infinity kW' card (2026-06-28). people > 4 → tankless recommendation. PlumbCalc.tsx WaterHeaterSizer renders household/peakDemandGPM/tankRecommendation/tanklessRecommendation/firstHourRating/recommendation EXACTLY — fields verified aligned, no phantoms."
}
